@startuml
left to right direction
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam actorStyle awesome

title TunSociety - Admin Use Case Diagram

actor Admin

rectangle "TunSociety Administration" {
  usecase "Access admin dashboard" as UC_AdminDash
  usecase "View platform summary" as UC_Summary
  usecase "Browse platform users" as UC_BrowseUsers
  usecase "Update user role" as UC_UpdateRole
  usecase "Review audit logs" as UC_AuditLogs
  usecase "Open moderation review" as UC_OpenModeration
}

Admin --> UC_AdminDash
Admin --> UC_Summary
Admin --> UC_BrowseUsers
Admin --> UC_UpdateRole
Admin --> UC_AuditLogs
Admin --> UC_OpenModeration

note bottom
Admin-specific backend endpoints currently cover user listing
and audit log review. Admins also inherit moderator review rights
through the shared Admin / Moderator authorization policy.
end note
@enduml
